{"tid":1901620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"9月立法會選舉配票方案","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T17:56:28.000Z","uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b40415c1a34f1f7e6c4ce169be90fb2b3865c3cf","tid":1901620,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ff87482ed7ed7b0ecbd64430211673e094476c","tid":1901620,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"區議會一/二點都要比一席本土"},{"pid":"e760c7716eecd63e9f53a2ce36264b2fd0ffe8d8","tid":1901620,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b40415c1a34f1f7e6c4ce169be90fb2b3865c3cf","tid":1901620,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"其實都未知有咩人出嚟選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起派系，投邊個都好睇佢嘅個人實力同性格<br />\n如果白頭佬仲出嚟選<br />\n話知佢競選邊一席，我一律唔投佢"},{"pid":"e23ee9cc2ce550cf193e822a67899575733dab00","tid":1901620,"uid":276293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩叫配票? ............"},{"pid":"e7663fb14619cf1534bfa129fdc5539d07457c45","tid":1901620,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"[歷史假想] 如果當年台灣一早有熱狗日日叫人投白票的話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdsHMS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdsHMS</a>"},{"pid":"a19eb9cc6a5020fea8c9fb007a2f0d1fce62cd38","tid":1901620,"uid":260023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T18:14:18.000Z","msg":"香港唯一能走的方向<br />\n抗爭是要寸土必爭的<br />\n成功是要有目標和過程的不是一步能登天!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贏功能組別 ---&gt; 贏立法會 ---&gt; 贏特首選委 ---&gt; 香港人自己選擇特首<br />\n先有機會走下一步</span></span> (立法會普選和特首普選 )<br />\n <br />\n可惜現在整個社會<br />\n也不能專注目標和行動<br />\n最好能做組織義工隊(幫他們直接填表)<br />\n順便組織黃色經濟圈(幫助他們宣傳)<br />\n例如生意很差的飲食界+組織勞工界+組織體育 演藝 文化 出版界<br />\n飲食界 勞工界(成立工會) 體育演藝文化界( 開體育 演藝)團體<br />\n <br />\n有朋友整左一個AI 極度快速幫你登記功能組別（已更新全部功能組別）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893858</a><br />\n <br />\n[善用區議會大勝成果] 區議員聯合搞公投, 搞泛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想成功必須先搞好選民登記</span></span><br />\n地區直選和功能組別<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攻破這九個功能組別</span></span><br />\n香港人便會真正面對共產黨的選擇一國一制<br />\n還是一國兩制<br />\n1.飲食界<br />\n2.進出口界<br />\n3.工程界<br />\n4.批發及零售界<br />\n5.紡織及製衣界<br />\n6.建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界<br />\n7.勞工界 （3席)<br />\n攻破這九個功能組別<br />\n <br />\n 若果沒有理解錯誤<br />\n飲食界 勞工界(成立工會) 體育演藝文化界( 開體育 演藝)團體 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">七個人可以&lt;開七個工會&gt;</span></span><br />\n還可以找<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(六個人)一齊做基本的種子</span></span><br />\n這樣有一個人加六個(6+1)<br />\n這樣便可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一人</span></span>可開一個公會(6+1)<br />\n六個人無限加入公會(6+1)<br />\n<br />\n3個人( 開體育 演藝)團體  (2個人)一齊做基本的種子  2+1 <br />\n<br />\n玩謝功能組別! 趕及明年特首選委選舉! <br />\n<br />\n原來只要營運咗一年既公司，申請個進出口牌，就可以做進出口界選民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1881201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1881201</a><br />\n<br />\n我有朋友整左一個AI 極度快速幫你登記功能組別（已更新全部功能組別）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893858</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會地區直選嘅目標<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1900897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1900897</a><br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係連登講<br />\n自己入工會<br />\n落街幫手叫黃店參與<br />\n<br />\n［叫黃店登記］民間記者會：《一日一界別 &mdash; 飲食界》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1901797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1901797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n功能組別我地寸土必爭，目標係過半議席拎否決權<br />\n<br />\n功能組別最後一個月！決勝關鍵係工程、建築測量、飲食、批發零售、進出口！（附懶人包）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/atdRoLV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/atdRoLV</a>"},{"pid":"be11d4d2cc0a5060992f17c316af6fdf31ec8488","tid":1901620,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b40415c1a34f1f7e6c4ce169be90fb2b3865c3cf","tid":1901620,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T03:47:52.000Z","msg":"想贏就要配票，如6張名單；<br />\n1.分性別，男投某3張，女投某3張<br />\n2.再分時期，五六七後投泛民，八九十後投本土<br />\n再分出生年，單數年投A，雙數年投B"},{"pid":"a7ee0e9d5f97a63e60b89461e052f413dfffd038","tid":1901620,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"負皮講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f50df0f4fd597f535dfc00f2a4f3617869bb7f","tid":1901620,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96ff87482ed7ed7b0ecbd64430211673e094476c","tid":1901620,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"區議會一/二點都要比一席本土"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"小圈子選舉 非本土強項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本土 應全數讓畀 泛民 去功能界別 奪權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n選民應全數支持 本土 去進攻 地區直選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}